{"name":"Garrotting Gas","permission":{"default":0,"HJtvMnewDM77SRUs":3},"type":"consumable","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This gas produces a choking or suffocating sensation, which, given the fact it's colorless, can be quite dangerous. A creature that inhales this poison must succeed on a DC 13 Constitution saving throw or be poisoned for 1 hour. If the saving throw fails by 5 or more, the creature is unconscious while poisoned in this way. The creature wakes up if it takes damage or a creature shakes it awake as an action.</p>\n<p>As an action, you can throw a bottle of Garrotting Gas at a point up to 60 feet away, releasing the gas and exposing creatures within 5 feet of that point.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"WRB pg 41","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":0,"attuned":false,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"Common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":5,"width":null,"units":"ft","type":""},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"charges","autoDestroy":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"con","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":null,"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":13,"scaling":"flat"},"consumableType":"potion"},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"RaV7n9CmzTKtBfPg"}
